h Microsoft channels such as Microsoft\u202F365 Copilot, Microsoft\u202FTeams, or the Entra Agent Registry ([learn.microsoft.com](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/overview)).\n\nSecurity, Governance & Enterprise Readiness  \n- Designed with enterprise governance in mind, Foundry Agent Service supports identity controls, network isolation, data residency, and bring-your-own Azure resources (e.g., Cosmos\u202FDB, Azure AI Search) for compliance ([learn.microsoft.com](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/overview)).  \n- Guardrails are built-in to mitigate unsafe outputs and prompt injection attacks, with Responsible AI guidance and integration available ([learn.microsoft.com](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/overview)).\n\nManagement, Observability & Control Plane  \n- The service includes capabilities for observing and managing agent behavior: Foundry Control Plane offers end‑to‑end observability, enhancing developer productivity and enterprise trust ([windowsmode.com](https://www.windowsmode.com/microsoft-and-nvidia-gtc-scaling-ai-with-foundry-azure-ai-physical-ai/)).  \n- It supports multi-agent orchestration and event-driven workflows, enabling robust enterprise automation scenarios across industries like customer support and data analysis ([latenode.com](https://latenode.com/blog/ai-agents-autonomous-systems/enterprise-ai-agent-solutions/microsoft-azure-ai-foundry-agent-service-2025-complete-review-implementation-guide)).\n\nSummary of Key Features  \n- Fully managed cloud-native platform for AI agents with SDKs in Python, C#, TypeScript  \n- Rich tool ecosystem: built-in tools, MCP, OpenAPI, A2A (agent-to-agent)  \n- Support for hosted containerized agents with auto-scaling and observability  \n- Streamlined deployment via Azure Developer CLI and Azure tooling  \n- Publishing capabilities for durable endpoint exposure and secure distribution  \n- Enterprise-grade security, governance, and compliance features  \n- Observability through Foundry Control Plane and support for complex, multi-agent workflows\n\nFoundry Agent Service is Microsoft's flagship platform for building intelligent agentic systems in enterprise contexts. It brings together powerful AI models, tools, governance, and deployment infrastructure to enable production-grade agent experiences that are secure, scalable, and integrable with existing enterprise systems.","annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://thirdeyedata.ai/technologies/azure-ai-foundry-agent-service","start_index":646,"end_index":734,"title":"Azure AI Foundry Agent Service: Tool for Deploying AI Agents"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://thirdeyedata.ai/technologies/azure-ai-foundry-agent-service","start_index":956,"end_index":1044,"title":"Azure AI Foundry Agent Service: Tool for Deploying AI Agents"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://microsoft.github.io/aitour26-WRK540-unlock-your-agents-potential-with-model-context-protocol/agent-service-overview/","start_index":1317,"end_index":1466,"title":"AI Foundry Agent Services - Unlock your Agents Potential with MCP"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://microsoft.github.io/build-your-first-agent-with-azure-ai-agent-service-workshop/","start_index":1642,"end_index":1755,"title":"Build your code-first agent with Azure AI Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/concepts/tool-catalog","start_index":2017,"end_index":2118,"title":"Agent tools overview for Microsoft Foundry Agent Service - Microsoft ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/concepts/tool-catalog","start_index":2267,"end_index":2368,"title":"Agent tools overview for Microsoft Foundry Agent Service - Microsoft ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/concepts/hosted-agents","start_index":2744,"end_index":2846,"title":"Hosted agents in Foundry Agent Service (preview) - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://visualstudiomagazine.com/articles/2025/11/19/azure-developer-cli-adds-ai-agent-extension-for-foundry-deployments.aspx","start_index":3085,"end_index":3240,"title":"Azure Developer CLI Adds AI Agent Extension for Foundry Deployments"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/how-to/publish-agent","start_index":3477,"end_index":3577,"title":"Publish agents in Microsoft Foundry - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/overview","start_index":3727,"end_index":3815,"title":"What is Microsoft Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/overview","start_index":4081,"end_index":4169,"title":"What is Microsoft Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/foundry/agents/overview","start_index":4311,"end_index":4399,"title":"What is Microsoft Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.windowsmode.com/microsoft-and-nvidia-gtc-scaling-ai-with-foundry-azure-ai-physical-ai/","start_index":4634,"end_index":4753,"title":"Microsoft and NVIDIA GTC: Scaling AI with Foundry, Azure AI & Physical ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://latenode.com/blog/ai-agents-autonomous-systems/enterprise-ai-agent-solutions/microsoft-azure-ai-foundry-agent-service-2025-complete-review-implementation-guide","start_index":4931,"end_index":5116,"title":"Microsoft Azure AI Foundry Agent Service 2025: Complete Review ..."}],"logprobs":[]}],"status":"completed"},"output_index":1,"sequence_number":76}

